last_episode_to_air.name: Butch Cassidy's Buried Secrets
last_episode_to_air.overview: Christof uncovers new clues about the true fate of Wild West outlaws Butch Cassidy and the Sundance Kid. He travels to the highlands of Bolivia and the mountains of Utah to dig up evidence that may finally solve this 100-year-old mystery.

name: Mission Declassified
overview: Seasoned investigative reporter Christof Putzel employs his tried and true information-gathering method — using declassified government documents — to explore legendary and notorious mysteries.

episodes.name: Escape from Alcatraz
episodes.overview: Three prisoners escaped from Alcatraz in 1962. Officially, they died in the surrounding waters, but FBI files say otherwise. Christof Putzel braves those same waters to hunt down inside information before going on a manhunt to Brazil.

episodes.name: The Hunt for D.B. Cooper
episodes.overview: Christof jumps from a plane and digs up rare FBI files as he follows shocking new leads that take him from the Pacific Northwest to Las Vegas and Utah in his quest to find the real identity of hijacker D.B. Cooper.

episodes.name: The Lindbergh Kidnapping
episodes.overview: Christof investigates the Lindbergh kidnapping, a story that made his grandfather's journalism career. Now, using his grandfather's notes and recently declassified FBI files, Christof tracks down surprising new leads to Germany and even the Nazi Party.

episodes.name: Boston's Unsolved Art Heist
episodes.overview: Christof investigates the robbery of the Isabella Stewart Gardner Museum, the largest art heist in history. In pursuit of the stolen masterpieces, he follows leads from dangerous members of organized crime that take him from Boston to Florida and France.

episodes.name: Decoding America's UFO Secrets
episodes.overview: Christof heads to the woods of the UK and snowy fields of Canada to determine what the truth is behind UFO sightings. He soon uncovers a much bigger story behind what secrets the government is hiding.

episodes.name: The Axe Man of New Orleans
episodes.overview: Christof tries to unmask the Axeman of New Orleans, a crazed murderer responsible for one of the deadliest unsolved killing sprees in American history. He uncovers a connection with organized crime and finds that this gruesome executioner may not have acted alone.

episodes.name: The Black Dahlia Murder
episodes.overview: Christof digs into the most infamous -- and gruesome -- unsolved murder case in Los Angeles history. He uncovers an investigation derailed by corruption and finds a confession pointing him to a new suspect in the Philippines.

episodes.name: The Lost Treasure of Dutch Schultz
episodes.overview: Christof joins the decades-long hunt for the buried millions of notorious gangster Dutch Schultz. With rare documents, exclusive interviews and cutting-edge tech, Christof tracks the Prohibition-era mob boss to find his ill-gotten haul of cash, gold and jewels.
